s://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=150&verse=4'>Psa 150:4</a><p/><b>Trumpets</b><p/><b>(a) Used in War</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=9'>Num 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=6'>Num 31:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=4'>Jos 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=27'>Jdg 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=34'>Jdg 6:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=3'>1Sa 13:3</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=28'>2Sa 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=1'>2Sa 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=12'>2Ch 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=24'>Job 39:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=3'>Eze 33:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=8'>1Co 14:8</a><p/><b>(b) Used in Worship</b> and celebrations<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=9'>Lev 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=10'>Num 10:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=34'>1Ki 1:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=13'>2Ki 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=14'>2Ki 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=12'>2Ch 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=28'>2Ch 20:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=26'>2Ch 29:26</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=10'>Ezr 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=35'>Neh 12:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=13'>Isa 27:13</a><p/><b>Viols</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=12'>Isa 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=14&verse=11'>Isa 14:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=23'>Amo 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=5'>Amo 6:5</a><p/><b>(3) Full Orchestra</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Sa 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=5'>1Ch 23:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=12'>2Ch 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=27'>2Ch 29:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=10'>Ezr 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=27'>Neh 12:27</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=25'>Psa 68:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=5'>Dan 3:5</a><p/><b>(B) MUSICIANS</b><p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=21'>Gen 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=16'>1Sa 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=7'>1Ch 25:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=12'>2Ch 34:12</a><p/><b>(2)</b> Players on Instruments<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=16'>1Sa 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=10'>1Sa 18:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=15'>2Ki 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=25'>Psa 68:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=32'>Eze 33:32</a><p/>-- Youthful. See YOUNG PEOPLE<p/><b>(C) SINGING</b><p/><b>(1)</b> A Religious Duty<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=1'>Psa 81:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=95&verse=1'>Psa 95:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=29'>Isa 30:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=15'>1Co 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=19'>Eph 5:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=16'>Col 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=13'>Jas 5:13</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Praise God, GRATITUDE<p/><b>(2) Examples of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=17'>Num 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=22'>2Ch 20:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=11'>Ezr 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=26'>Mar 14:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=25'>Act 16:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=9'>Rev 5:9</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Praise (2), GRATITUDE<p/>New Song, NEW MAN<p/><b>(D) ANCIENT CHOIRS</b><p/><b>Regularly Employed</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=33'>1Ch 9:33</a><p/><b>Assisted by an Orchestra</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=16'>1Ch 15:16</a><p/><b>Vested Choir led by Precentor</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=27'>1Ch 15:27</a><p/><b>A Great Chorus Choir</b> God gave to Heman fourteen sons and three<p/>daughters<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=6'>1Ch 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=7'>1Ch 25:7</a><p/><b>A Militant Choir,</b> songs lead to victory<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=21'>2Ch 20:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ch 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=15'>2Ch 35:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=65'>Ezr 2:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=42'>Neh 12:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=8'>Ecc 2:8</a><p/><b>(E) SONGS</b><p/><b>(1) Idle</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=12'>Psa 69:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=23'>Amo 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=5'>Amo 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=8&verse=10'>Amo 8:10</a><p/><b>(2) In the night</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=35&verse=10'>Job 35:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=8'>Psa 42:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=77&verse=6'>Psa 77:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=149&verse=5'>Psa 149:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=29'>Isa 30:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=25'>Act 16:25</a><p/><b>(3) Of Victory</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=1'>Exo 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=5&verse=1'>Jdg 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=14&verse=3'>Rev 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=15&verse=3'>Rev 15:3</a>"}]}